## 6. Core Features — What Users Can Actually Do

### Customer Flow
```
Landing Page → Browse Categories → Shop Page → Filter/Search → Add to Cart → Checkout → Receipt
```

1. **Register / Login** — Modal pop-ups on the home page. JWT token + user object stored in `localStorage`.
2. **Role-based redirect** — Admins go to `admin.html`, regular users go to `shop.html` after login.
3. **Browse & Filter** — Products load from the API. Filter by category via pill buttons or search by name/description client-side.
4. **Cart** — Slide-in panel from the right. Add items, remove items, see running total. Cart badge on the icon updates live.
5. **Stock awareness** — "Out of Stock" badge on product cards; Add to Cart button is disabled if `stock === 0`.
6. **Checkout (COD)** — Fill in name, phone, address. On confirm → POST to `/orders` → cart cleared → receipt modal shown.
7. **Guest Checkout** — Works without an account (`user_id: null` is sent).
8. **My Orders** — Logged-in users can view their order history with status badges (Pending/Processing/Shipping/Delivered).
9. **Delete Profile** — Users can permanently delete their own account from the user dropdown.
10. **Logout** — Clears `localStorage`, redirects to home.

