## 9. Known Gaps & Potential Improvements

> [!NOTE]
> These are observations — not criticisms. For a learning project / MVP, this is solid work.

| Gap | Impact | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| No auth middleware on backend routes | High — product deletion/creation unprotected | Add `authenticateAdmin` middleware using `jwt.verify()` |
| Cart is in-memory (resets on refresh) | Medium | Use `localStorage` to persist cart |
| No payment gateway | Low for COD, High for online payment | Integrate Stripe / JazzCash |
| No image upload | Medium — images require external URLs | Add Multer + Cloudinary for uploads |
| No input sanitization/validation | Medium | Use `express-validator` or `zod` |
| `DELETE /user/:id` has no auth check | High — anyone can delete any user by ID | Require JWT + match user ID |
| CORS set to `*` | Low-Medium | Restrict to your frontend domain in production |
| No pagination on `/products` | Low now, High at scale | Add `LIMIT` / `OFFSET` query params |
